text:
Big changes continue at Twitter: Company to lay off 8 percent of engineers 
Published By: Macworld.com - Today 
Twitter will lay off up to one in 12 employees as it streamlines its product roadmap, new CEO Jack Dorsey told his workforce on Tuesday morn...
